#ROOM
Vnum     38052
Name     &xThe Bulwark - West Entrance&d~
Sector   field~
Flags    ~
Desc     A massive barricade of sharpened logs and stone blocks marks the 
border between the safety of Tirisfal and the horror of the 
Plaguelands. Soldiers of the Argent Dawn stand firm here, 
watching the eastern horizon for any movement. The air is 
thick with a yellow, sulfurous mist that burns the throat.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11699
Desc      Return to the Tirisfal Glades.~
#ENDEXIT
