#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     38053
Name     &xThe Sullied Path&d~
Sector   field~
Flags    ~
Desc     A wide, cracked stone road leading through a valley of dead 
trees. The bark of the trees is grey and peeling, and no 
birds sing in their branches. To the north, a small trail 
winds up toward a ruined farmstead.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    38052
Desc      Return to the Bulwark.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    38054
Desc      The road continues east.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    38058
Desc      The path to Felstone Field.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 38015 5 38053
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     38054
Name     &xThe Blighted Crossroads&d~
Sector   field~
Flags    ~
Desc     The road splits here. To the north lies the gated community 
of Hearthglen, while to the east, the ruined city of 
Andorhal dominates the horizon. A Scourge plague cauldron 
sits in a nearby field, emitting a constant stream of 
toxic gas.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    38053
Desc      Western Sullied Path.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    38070
Desc      The gates of Andorhal.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    38090
Desc      The road to Hearthglen.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    38062
Desc      The path to Dalson's Tears.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 38014 1 38054
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     38055
Name     &xThe Ruined Bulwark Tower&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    ~
Desc     A high stone tower at the western edge of the Plaguelands. 
The top has been blown off by some ancient magical explosion, 
leaving a jagged stone crown that provides an excellent 
view of the surrounding blight.
~
#EXIT
Direction down~
ToRoom    38052
Desc      The Bulwark.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 38020 5 38055
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     38056
Name     &xArgent Dawn Command Post&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    ~
Desc     A small collection of tents and crates near the Bulwark. 
Commander Ashlam Valormane stands here, planning the 
Dawn's next move against the cauldrons.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    38052
Desc      The Bulwark.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 38012 1 38056
Reset O 0 38030 5 38056
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     38057
Name     &xThe Gryphon Roost - West&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    ~
Desc     A flat stone landing on the Bulwark wall. Several gryphons 
rest here, ready to carry messages back to Stormwind or 
Ironforge.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    38052
Desc      The Bulwark.~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     38058
Name     &xFelstone Field - Entrance&d~
Sector   field~
Flags    ~
Desc     A large farm that has been completely consumed by the 
plague. The soil is black and oily, and the crops have 
