~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    38053
Desc      The sullied path.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    38059
Desc      The Felstone Farmhouse.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 38000 5 38058
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     38059
Name     &xThe Felstone Farmhouse&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The interior of the house is a mess of broken furniture and 
shattered glass. Skeletal flayers lurk in the shadows of 
the kitchen and upstairs bedrooms.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    38058
Desc      The field entrance.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 38000 5 38059
Reset O 0 38036 5 38059
#ENDROOM

