Vnum     38060
Name     &xFelstone Field - The Cauldron&d~
Sector   field~
Flags    ~
Desc     A massive Scourge cauldron sits in the center of the field, 
bubbling with a luminous green liquid. A skeletal mage carefully monitors the mixture.
~
